column5: Located 10 minutes north of Hwy 121/Main street. You will have a spacious room and a private bathroom. 1 mile from Hidden Cove Park/Marina and 6 miles from Cottonwood Park. Multiple shopping centers: Costco, Walmart, Kroger, Best Buy, Target, Aldi's, Home Depot, Lowe's, Restaurants and Bars!
column8: New cozy house with spacious room (King bed)
